<http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#ClassI> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#disjointWith> <http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#ClassIIb> .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#ClassI> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Devices with minimal risk to patient safety, such as non-electronic walking aids, bandages, or simple surgical instruments."@en .
<http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#ClassI> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Class I"@en .
