<http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#ImplantableActive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A powered device introduced totally or partially into the body via surgery or medical intervention (including natural orifices) and intended to remain there after the procedure."@en .
