<http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#SelfTest> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#DeviceType> .
