<http://www.semanticweb.org/bea/ontologies/2026/3clasificacion_MDR_IVDR#UserNotice> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "It is an official communication from a manufacturer to users informing them of a safety risk with a medical device and providing instructions to prevent harm."@en .
